<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ludwig<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> grafen
                        zu <expan>Öting<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Wolgeborne<ex>n</ex></expan> und lieben
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> als uns ewr gnade vor und auch yeczunt
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie ewch <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Mangolt, <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan>, fürbracht hab von des
                                <expan>gew<ex>er</ex>bs</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz er an uns getan hab als
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> der messe <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ze <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan>, darauf ewr edell an uns begert, ewch
                        von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>zolln<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> wissen und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> ze
                        laszen etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> nehsten
                                <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>,
                        daz wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> selbs
                            <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        edell <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit ewch davon ze reden. Also
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch wir das
                                <expan>kurczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> tun. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> Christi. </ab>
